│  (LLM-as-a-Judge, Role-Based Multi-Agent Collaboration, Reflection Loops, Tool-Using Agents) are largely consistent with other sources and document          │
│  insights regarding current or emerging practices, the future publication date reduces the credibility of this specific source as evidence for *currently*   │
│  common patterns. The severity of this conflict is assessed as Medium, as it primarily affects the temporal validity of the claim rather than the existence  │
│  or relevance of the patterns themselves, which are corroborated by other sources.                                                                           │
